世界贸易中心于1966年在一片[[填海地|填海地]]上奠基，其地表下方{{convert|65|m|ft}}为基岩<ref name="iglauer">{{cite news|title=The Biggest Foundation|author=Iglauer, Edith|date=November 4, 1972|magazine=The New Yorker}}</ref>。在施工工程中使用了全新的[[地下连续墙|地下连续墙]]施工技巧以防止[[哈德孙河|哈德孙河]]的水渗入工地。在基地的开挖和{{tsl|en|Construction of One World Trade Center|世界貿易中心一號大樓工程|世贸中心工程}}中，原下城哈德孙隧道继续在抬高的隧道中维持运营。原哈德孙总站于1971年新[[纽新捷运|纽新捷运]]线路完工后关闭<ref name="NYT1968">{{cite news|author=Carroll, Maurice|title=A Section of the Hudson Tubes is Turned into Elevated Tunnel|date=December 30, 1968|newspaper=New York Times|page=33|url=https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F40F10FB355C147493C2AA1789D95F4C8685F9|accessdate=May 30, 2010|archive-date=2014-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325192414/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F40F10FB355C147493C2AA1789D95F4C8685F9}}</ref>。新站的造价为当时的3500万美元。车站启用后，每日的客流为85,000人次<ref name="NYT1971">{{cite news|title=Air-Cooled PATH Terminal in World Trade Center Opens Tuesday|date=July 1, 1971|newspaper=New York Times|page=94|url=https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=FB0717FD3A5B1A7493C3A9178CD85F458785F9|accessdate=May 30, 2010|archive-date=2014-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325190638/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=FB0717FD3A5B1A7493C3A9178CD85F458785F9}}</ref>。

新的纽新捷运车站于1971年7月6日于异地开放<ref>{{cite news|title=New PATH Station Opens Downtown|author=Burks, Edward C.|date=July 7, 1971|newspaper=New York Times|page=74|url=https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F00910FB3A5B1A7493C5A9178CD85F458785F9|accessdate=May 30, 2010|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103074111/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F00910FB3A5B1A7493C5A9178CD85F458785F9}}</ref>。[[灯泡线|灯泡线]]上更大的站台使其能够容纳10节编组的列车，远高于原先仅能容纳6编组列车的舊站<ref name="NYT1968" />。当{{tsl|en|Construction of One World Trade Center|世界貿易中心一號大樓工程|世贸中心工程}}接近尾声时，车站修建了连接车站和[[教堂街|教堂街]]的便道。车站开放后，站台和站厅間设有9部高速电梯连接<ref name="NYT1971" />。新的世界贸易中心纽新捷运车站有[[霍博肯－世界贸易中心线|霍博肯－世界贸易中心线]]和[[纽瓦克－世界贸易中心线|纽瓦克－世界贸易中心线]]经过，而车站和世界贸易中心之间则通过地下行人通道和{{tsl|en|Westfield World Trade Center|西田世界貿易中心|一座商场}}连接。车站同时还有连接[[纽约地铁|纽约地铁]]{{NYCS trains|Eighth south|bold}}[[錢伯斯街-世界貿易中心／公園廣場車站|世界贸易中心车站]]和{{NYCS trains|Broadway south|bold}}[[科特蘭街車站_(BMT百老匯線)|科特蘭街車站]]的地下通道。到了2001年，车站日均進出旅客25,000人次<ref>{{cite news|title=Next Stop, Semi-Normalcy|newspaper=The Star-Ledger|location=Newark|date=September 13, 2001|author=Wyckoff, P.L. and Rudy Larini}}</ref>。

车站虽然在[[1993年世界貿易中心爆炸案|1993年世界貿易中心爆炸案]]中因天花板脱落砸伤数十人，但车站本身并未受到严重损毁<ref>{{cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CE3DB103AF934A15751C0A965958260|title=Blast Hits Trade Center, Bomb Suspected; 5 Killed, Thousands Flee Smoke In Towers|first=|date=February 27, 1993|work=|newspaper=New York Times|access-date=December 13, 2016|via=|author=McFadden, Robert D.}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Now, the Cleanup, Work begins assessing the damage|newspaper=Newsday|location=New York|date=February 28, 1993|author=Newkirk, Pamela}}</ref>。纽新港务局在爆炸案发生一周内恢复了车站的纽新捷运服务<ref>{{cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CE7DC133AF932A35750C0A965958260|title=PATH and Subway Service Is Being Restored|first=Peter|date=March 1, 1993|work=|newspaper=New York Times|access-date=December 13, 2016|via=|author=Marks}}</ref>。

2001年9月11日，纽新港务局在恐攻期間第一架飞机——[[美國航空11號班機恐怖襲擊|美國航空11號班機]]撞上世贸大厦北塔后关闭了车站。在8：46分飛機撞擊北塔時，有3列纽新捷运列车正在进入车站，其中1列来自纽瓦克，另外两列来自霍博肯。第一列来自霍博肯的列车进站后未作停留及旅客乘降便立刻折返。第二列来自霍博肯的列车于8：53分停靠3號軌，被勒令靠站接驳雇员。但这列火车从未离开世界贸易中心大楼，2001年晚些时候在漫长的救援过程中尋獲。来自纽瓦克的列車于8：55分进站，在接驳乘客后离开。另外有一列空车于9：10分停靠车站，在接载纽新捷运员工和一些流浪汉后驶离，之后车站宣布关闭<ref>{{cite news|title=Quick-Acting P.A. Steered 5,000 Commuters to Safety|newspaper=The Star-Ledger|location=Newark|date=September 19, 2001|author=Schwaneberg, Robert}}</ref>，隨後在{{link-en|世界貿易中心倒塌|Collapse of the World Trade Center|世貿中心倒塌}}期間被摧毀<ref>{{cite web | author=The Associated Press | title=Decisive action by PATH employees kept 9/11 riders from danger | website=NJ.com | date=August 20, 2011 | url=http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/08/decisive_action_by_path_employ.html | access-date=July 6, 2018 | archive-date=2014-03-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307025234/http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/08/decisive_action_by_path_employ.html }}</ref>。

===临时车站===
